      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">5</infon>
        <offset>660</offset>
        <text>Sinking particles, on the other hand, also scavenge iron from solution.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">6</infon>
        <offset>732</offset>
        <text>The balance between these supply and removal processes determines the concentration of dissolved iron in the ocean.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">7</infon>
        <offset>848</offset>
        <text>Whether this balance, and many other facets of the biogeochemical cycle, will change as the climate warms remains to be seen.
</text>
      </sentence>
